Subject: [Bioc-devel] Updated Badges/Shields on Landing Pages
Message-ID: <MW2PR12MB236491B9322F36E628553D03F9010@MW2PR12MB2364.namprd12.prod.outlook.com>

The package landing page badges have undergone a few updates over the last few days.

There has been the addition of an updated badge reflecting the last commit date that can have values of today, < 1 week, < 1 month, < 3 months, since release, before release.

The workflows now have badges for build, download, and updated.

The downloads badge has been updated to reflect a ranking based on number of
